snippet.title: Disney Dreamlight Valley – The Lucky Dragon Update Trailer
snippet.description:
Join Mulan and Mushu in the latest Realm! As a new recruit, assist Mushu around the Training Camp and hone your skills with Mulan in tests that will challenge your strength, precision, and endurance.  
Decorate with beautiful blooming magnolias, dress in elegant silk fashions, and claim new rewards in the new Majesty and Magnolias Star Path.

Play Disney Dreamlight Valley now: https://disneydreamlightvalley.com/getnow
Learn more about The Lucky Dragon update: https://disneydreamlightvalley.com/news/TheLuckyDragonUpdate

Join the community on:
Instagram: http://instagram.com/disneydreamlightvalley 
Twitter: http://twitter.com/DisneyDLV 
Facebook: http://facebook.com/DisneyDreamlightValley
